  "content": "<p><strong>Second Day of Christmas: Gift Guide</strong></p>\n<p><em>♫ On the second day of Christmas, Katie Crafts gave to me- A gift guide filled with artists from Etsy! ♫</em></p>\n<p>Today is our second day of Christmas, so that means more festive fun! <strong>Natalia Khon</strong> of <a title=\"Natalia's Jewellry on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/shop/nataliasjewellery\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>Natalia’s Jewellry</strong></a> made us a beautiful treasury for today’s post, filled with fabulous items from Etsy that will surely put you in the holiday spirit!</p>\n<p>Like something you see above? Here are all the Etsy shops so you can visit them!</p>\n<ol>\n<li><a title=\"Janie Champagnie on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/170378564/faux-gingerbread-train-a-holiday-express?ref=tre-2724518341-1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Janie Champagnie</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"ZHAVI Knitwear on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/212554580/crochet-snowflake-christmas-present?ref=tre-2724518341-2\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ZHAVI Knitwear</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Imagine Event Boutique on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/209883145/rustic-christmas-themescape?ref=tre-2724518341-3\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Imagine Event Boutique</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Victoria Semykina on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/163074938/on-sale-deer-art-black-and-white-print?ref=tre-2724518341-4\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Victoria Semykina</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Boots N Gus on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/72652973/cascading-autumns-acorns-crystal-clear?ref=tre-2724518341-5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Boots N Gus</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Old West Gallery on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/204147616/spirit-of-the-bear-by-thomas-kinkade?ref=tre-2724518341-6\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Old West Gallery</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Veda on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/164384477/100-natural-facial-serum?ref=tre-2724518341-7\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Veda</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Fancy Knittles on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/175390383/snowman-with-big-heart-button-christmas?ref=tre-2724518341-8\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Fancy Knittles</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"CMyUniqueCreations on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/211887263/crocheted-doily-15-inch-elegant?ref=tre-2724518341-9\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">CMyUniqueCreations</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Accessodium on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/212389037/chunky-infinity-scarf-knit-chunky?ref=tre-2724518341-10\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Accessodium</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Look4Wood on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/195916704/wooden-plate-handmade-home-decor-fruit?ref=tre-2724518341-11\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Look4Wood</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Florasense on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/57654672/christmas-wreath-candle-ring-advent?ref=tre-2724518341-12\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Florasense</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Colored Yarn on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/198077385/xmas-sale-25-crocheted-art-doll-elf?ref=tre-2724518341-13\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Colored Yarn</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Gneiss Spice on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/84911092/magnetic-spice-rack-includes-24-organic?ref=tre-2724518341-14\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Gneiss Spice</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Sunny Chocolate on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/211813614/assorti-6-candies-box-raw-chocolate?ref=tre-2724518341-15\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Sunny Chocolate</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Viya's Wickerworks on Etsy\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/185554377/christmas-gift-idea-woven-nesting-basket?ref=tre-2724518341-16\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Viya’s Wickerworks</a></li>\n</ol>\n<p>Thanks so much for the wonderful gift guide, <strong>Natalia! </strong>Don’t forget to check out <strong>Natalia</strong>‘s own <strong><a title=\"Natalia Khon Jewellry on Facebook\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/shop/nataliasjewellery\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><em>Etsy shop</em></a></strong> for more great ideas!</p>\n<p>What is your favorite item above?</p>\n",
